{"tid":1074100,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解經濟學好似仲複雜過科學?","createTime":"2019-03-23T07:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T13:38:34.000Z","uid":149496,"like":3,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"900148d29cfb6aaa58a855b53bb7952946b0785f","tid":1074100,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"永遠都唔會有controlled environment俾你做實驗 啲專家都好似搞唔清楚實際環境<br />\n結果啲問題好似都係推俾將來嘅人黎搞"},{"pid":"101563af9da186b31b666a900cf74ce1ef74a35e","tid":1074100,"uid":242921,"like":13,"dislike":37,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"經濟學是鳩吹，所以好多經濟要加好多數去證明，變咗好Q複雜。<br />\n<br />\n利申：會考Econ A"},{"pid":"504c4d699c50752a3bdbcf3bf9edf357cb4dc3b2","tid":1074100,"uid":52609,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:15:06.000Z","msg":"社會科學研究嘅係人，人咁鬼煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1422fc288618f3b4f3a67bb94bb2777119467006","tid":1074100,"uid":21699,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b33de4fd5698b42929bca85fb92846ab39f9ba","tid":1074100,"uid":76098,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n高考讀唔掂econ 到而家都好憎好不解econ"},{"pid":"aaf9cc8373b0fbe754ac3f1164c2bae2161aaa99","tid":1074100,"uid":61692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"冇讀過econ, 留名學野"},{"pid":"30a94c8b77255edb830ef6ce49a0523dcb1250a7","tid":1074100,"uid":149496,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1b33de4fd5698b42929bca85fb92846ab39f9ba","tid":1074100,"uid":76098,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n高考讀唔掂econ 到而家都好憎好不解econ"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:09:31.000Z","msg":"我就係想有人傾下經濟學 有冇有學識嘅巴打可以講下<br />\n例如講下凱因斯主義 新自由主義 等等點樣應用係現實當中"},{"pid":"50c0bb52af7a1fdb749433504c89ea44f73f8705","tid":1074100,"uid":49813,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"900148d29cfb6aaa58a855b53bb7952946b0785f","tid":1074100,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"永遠都唔會有controlled environment俾你做實驗 啲專家都好似搞唔清楚實際環境<br />\n結果啲問題好似都係推俾將來嘅人黎搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"正如你所講<br />\nEcon無得做experiment <br />\n好多variables 都互相有影響 但無得透過人為實驗Test 因果關係<br />\n<br />\n家陣經濟學家研究一個宏觀問題<br />\n好多時都係用舊data睇d關係<br />\n或者用簡化既assumptions 去砌model出來predict 或解釋下現象<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢講話複雜過自然科學<br />\n但肯定既係現實環境既複雜同令經濟學家好難全盤知道件事既原因同結果<br />\n再加上人會變 同埋有expectation 既存在<br />\n導致同一個policy tool今日用同他日再用既結果有唔同"},{"pid":"7ca69161b2b8a556eb55b2de3f820cab4f21fccb","tid":1074100,"uid":81113,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"經濟學係人類行為學<br />\n<br />\n人類行為常變<br />\n<br />\n一般科學唔會常變<br />\n<br />\n點比？"},{"pid":"f048cdf87635fad459b81a4dae66e67956388665","tid":1074100,"uid":87339,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"有堆白痴以為經濟已經嚴謹到好似物理學咁 結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e7aceac1f1ab1aedf2a0a642cdbca3f372e302","tid":1074100,"uid":49813,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"30a94c8b77255edb830ef6ce49a0523dcb1250a7","tid":1074100,"uid":149496,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1b33de4fd5698b42929bca85fb92846ab39f9ba","tid":1074100,"uid":76098,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n高考讀唔掂econ 到而家都好憎好不解econ"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:09:31.000Z","msg":"我就係想有人傾下經濟學 有冇有學識嘅巴打可以講下<br />\n例如講下凱因斯主義 新自由主義 等等點樣應用係現實當中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"睇多左paper 同model就知道<br />\n其實D咩Keynesian啊  New Classical 啊 都係講緊佢地係咩用咩model framework 去解個Economy<br />\n唔同既assumption 唔同既framework下 個結果唔同 咪會有唔同既主義<br />\n<br />\n例如係高中Econ學簡單版本既Keynesian Model咪會見到<br />\nFiscal stimulus 點樣boost個Economy<br />\n但係又可能有人信 Ricardian Equivalence<br />\nFiscal stimulus 其實boost唔到個Economy<br />\n<br />\n好難話邊個岩邊個錯<br />\n因為empirical睇 D model 有時用得到 有時用唔到<br />\n又有時某D地方用得到 有時某D地方用唔到<br />\n唔一定係個model錯<br />\n只係本身D model係簡化左好多現實情況<br />\n所以好多時會按Case 係model上面做modification"},{"pid":"d887e999f046e82d0360403aeeea56c897ec53ce","tid":1074100,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec88cb67fe22ae245fec4ba8598ca4597351ef93","tid":1074100,"uid":78336,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"因為真係複雜過科學<br />\n除非你有辦法將人既所有行為都量化成數據<br />\n先有辦法做到"},{"pid":"76fc6e517b92a472fc8eee86210428caa242a7f9","tid":1074100,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d887e999f046e82d0360403aeeea56c897ec53ce","tid":1074100,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:38:40.000Z","msg":"String theory咪又係驗證唔到"},{"pid":"a1321046e8693723db39c3cc900a949d9010a06d","tid":1074100,"uid":192078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d887e999f046e82d0360403aeeea56c897ec53ce","tid":1074100,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">經濟學</span>是一門對產品和服務的生產、分配以及消費進行研究的<span style=\"color: red;\">社會科學</span>"},{"pid":"fe68898aeeff18edf3179303555646e76bb54305","tid":1074100,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ec88cb67fe22ae245fec4ba8598ca4597351ef93","tid":1074100,"uid":78336,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"因為真係複雜過科學<br />\n除非你有辦法將人既所有行為都量化成數據<br />\n先有辦法做到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"大數據 深度學習 人工智能 可以了～"},{"pid":"97ba8c5c73419fcea0175228834b2ed99fe531bb","tid":1074100,"uid":21203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:43:19.000Z","msg":"有&quot;人&quot; involve就會複雜"},{"pid":"c72d16e6522df7ad8df172b8c3506e4a26e33709","tid":1074100,"uid":49813,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f048cdf87635fad459b81a4dae66e67956388665","tid":1074100,"uid":87339,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"有堆白痴以為經濟已經嚴謹到好似物理學咁 結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:45:58.000Z","msg":"有堆唔識野既人以為Econ就係9up<br />\n<br />\n經濟學本身好嚴謹<br />\n大部份theory經得起數學既考驟<br />\n因為同物理學一樣都係向數學借tools<br />\n例如好多macro model都見到既Euler equation 已經係其中一個例子<br />\n只係經濟本身好難研究 無自然科學咁容易做testing 做experiment<br />\n物理學 有symmetry, translation in time, translation in space <br />\n你咩時候 咩地方做testing都出同一個Result<br />\n但經濟學唔同<br />\n人係會變 又有Expectation<br />\n所以出來既Result可以唔同"},{"pid":"ddddc9e3f8b271d5a1bab9e5d19fa2830c236b69","tid":1074100,"uid":29702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e6a4d7a2875b4a0705cfcaaf7782e629dff9cf5","tid":1074100,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea8a9ad8852bbd885a59ffb524442f11b197a39c","tid":1074100,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:53:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1483f1f4f65bbca8b23997cf6ad417ecb735f7f","tid":1074100,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"人是複雜的"},{"pid":"ce90d4db0e9344bc022cff4fb9cc9cf15085abb5","tid":1074100,"uid":49813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea8a9ad8852bbd885a59ffb524442f11b197a39c","tid":1074100,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e6a4d7a2875b4a0705cfcaaf7782e629dff9cf5","tid":1074100,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddddc9e3f8b27